    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This naturally aspirated masterpiece features a 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for unparalleled induction notes. This chassis is mechanically flawless: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, rod bearings were proactively replaced with VAC Motorsports coated shells, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with welded plates to mitigate stress fractures. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a refreshed M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true with zero bushing compliance issues, and the exterior retains its factory luster with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. A turn-key collector piece for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
