    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior is finished in a flawless deep metallic coat that has been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept; you will find zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is in pristine condition\u2014the premium leather bolsters remain firm with no signs of wear, the carpets are spotless, and it still retains that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with every service performed exclusively at the authorized dealership; a thick binder of full documentation is included. From the immaculate engine bay to the untouched wheels, this car is a collector-grade example meant for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
