    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every surface, mechanical component, and electronic system functions with the precision of a new assembly. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class. Available for immediate acquisition by those who accept nothing less than perfection.",
